<taxonomicName authorityName="Gray" authorityYear="1870" box="[473,621,1944,1968]" class="Anthozoa" family="Keratoisididae" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Alcyonacea" pageId="3" pageNumber="140" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="family">Keratoisididae</taxonomicName>
modified from 
<bibRefCitation author="Watling, L. &amp; Heestand Saucier, E. &amp; France, S. C." box="[785,1002,1944,1968]" pageId="3" pageNumber="140" pagination="337 - 375" refId="ref9546" refString="Watling, L. Heestand Saucier, E. &amp; France, S. C. (2022) Towards a revision of the bamboo corals: Part 4, delineating the family Keratoisididae. Zootaxa, 5093 (3), 337 - 375. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 5093.3.4" type="journal article" year="2022">Watling et al. (2022)</bibRefCitation>
. New taxa added in this paper are in bold lettering. Bootstrap values&gt;50 are shown above the nodes and Bayesian probability values&gt;0.5 are shown below the nodes. Major clades are referred to by the designation along the right side of the cladogram.
</paragraph>
</caption>
